                                                                                                                                Navigation

                                                                                                                                Navigation header

                                                                                                                                The navigation header is a top-anchored component that establishes the context of the screen and allows users to easily navigate through different flows.

                                                                                                                                Screen readers

                                                                                                                                VoiceOver

                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                1. Voiced preview: “Back, Button.”

                                                                                                                                Label: Back

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button


                                                                                                                                2. Voiced preview: “ Favorite, Button.”

                                                                                                                                Label: [Button label]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button


                                                                                                                                3. Voiced preview: “Share, Button.”

                                                                                                                                Label: [Button label]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Button


                                                                                                                                4. Voiced preview: “Restaurants, Heading.”

                                                                                                                                Label: [Title label]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Header

                                                                                                                                Talkback

                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                1. Voiced preview: “Navigate up, Button, Double-tap to activate.”

                                                                                                                                ContentDescription: Navigate up*

                                                                                                                                Role: Button

                                                                                                                                Action: Double-tap to activate.


                                                                                                                                2. Voiced preview: “ Favorite, Button, Double-tap to activate.”

                                                                                                                                ContentDescription: [Button label]

                                                                                                                                Role: Button

                                                                                                                                Action: Double-tap to activate.


                                                                                                                                3. Voiced preview: “Share, Button, Double-tap to activate.”

                                                                                                                                ContentDescription: [Button label]

                                                                                                                                Role: Button

                                                                                                                                Action: Double-tap to activate.


                                                                                                                                4. Voiced preview: “Restaurants, Heading.”

                                                                                                                                ContentDescription: [Title label]

                                                                                                                                Role: TextView, heading

                                                                                                                                On Android, the word "Back" is associated with the system's bottom navigation bar, which can take the user in and out of applications. "Navigate up" describes moving back in an application, but will never exit the app.
